1. Analysis: The market focuses on Powell's speech this week, and the expectation of interest rate cuts and the risk of global economic recession are still the focus;
2. Analysis: Some Ethereum inverse ETFs have risen sharply, and shorting ETH may become a hot spot for trading this year;
3. Phantom was sued for the theft of Wiener Doge Meme coins;
4. Galaxy Digital transferred 12,500 ETH and 5 million USDT to Binance;
5. The fourth batch of XRPfi was launched, and the upper limit of XRP deposits was 10 million;
6. A giant whale liquidated 14,227 ETH, with a cumulative profit of US$931,000;
7. In 2015, the Ethereum ICO whale sold 612 ETH again after two days, and still held 29,577 ETH;
8. A whale is selling 6.25 million Fartcoin and 10 million POPCAT with DCA;
9. Australian Monochrome Spot Bitcoin ETF holdings increased to 330 BTC;
10. Solana has implemented SIMD-0207, and the block limit has increased by 4%.
